columns.name: endpoint_name
columns.description: The name of the DevEndpoint.

columns.name: arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the DevEndpoint.

columns.name: status
columns.description: The current status of this DevEndpoint.

columns.name: availability_zone
columns.description: The AWS Availability Zone where this DevEndpoint is located.

columns.name: created_timestamp
columns.description: The point in time at which this DevEndpoint was created.

columns.name: extra_jars_s3_path
columns.description: The path to one or more Java .jar files in an S3 bucket that should be loaded in your DevEndpoint.

columns.name: extra_python_libs_s3_path
columns.description: The paths to one or more Python libraries in an Amazon S3 bucket that should be loaded in your DevEndpoint. Multiple values must be complete paths separated by a comma.

columns.name: failure_reason
columns.description: The reason for a current failure in this DevEndpoint.

columns.name: glue_version
columns.description: Glue version determines the versions of Apache Spark and Python that Glue supports.

columns.name: last_modified_timestamp
columns.description: The point in time at which this DevEndpoint was last modified.

columns.name: last_update_status
columns.description: The status of the last update.

columns.name: number_of_nodes
columns.description: The number of Glue Data Processing Units (DPUs) allocated to this DevEndpoint.

columns.name: number_of_workers
columns.description: The number of workers of a defined workerType that are allocated to the development endpoint.

columns.name: private_address
columns.description: A private IP address to access the DevEndpoint within a VPC if the DevEndpoint is created within one.

columns.name: public_address
columns.description: The public IP address used by this DevEndpoint. The PublicAddress field is present only when you create a non-virtual private cloud (VPC) DevEndpoint.

columns.name: public_key
columns.description: The public key to be used by this DevEndpoint for authentication.

columns.name: role_arn
columns.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM role used in this DevEndpoint.

columns.name: security_configuration
columns.description: The name of the SecurityConfiguration structure to be used with this DevEndpoint.

columns.name: subnet_id
columns.description: The subnet ID for this DevEndpoint.

columns.name: vpc_id
columns.description: The ID of the virtual private cloud (VPC) used by this DevEndpoint.

columns.name: worker_type
columns.description: The type of predefined worker that is allocated to the development endpoint. Accepts a value of Standard, G.1X, or G.2X.

columns.name: yarn_endpoint_address
columns.description: The YARN endpoint address used by this DevEndpoint.

columns.name: zeppelin_remote_spark_interpreter_port
columns.description: The Apache Zeppelin port for the remote Apache Spark interpreter.

columns.name: public_keys
columns.description: A list of public keys to be used by the DevEndpoints for authentication.

columns.name: security_group_ids
columns.description: A list of security group identifiers used in this DevEndpoint.
